  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section-gray">
  <div class="container narrow">
    <p class="section-number">08 · Why us</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Six reasons.</h2>

    <ul class="why-list">
      <li><strong>Igniter current measurement protocol.</strong> Inline clamp meter on live circuit. Most appliance shops skip the test and replace based on age. We test first.</li>
